column5: Here’s a fun video I made of my daughters first laker. We live up in northwest Ontario Hope you enjoy https://youtu.be/vAtHJzqUDco
That was better than watching a WWF match,thanks
Fun to watch! Great getting the young ones on fish. Thanks for sharing.
Nice fish, the memory of your daughter's trout will be with you forever! Time well spent!!!!!! Bill

This was wonderful. There is nothing like sharing a passion of a hobby with one of your kids. I just watched this with my fishing-nut daughter, and she loved it too. It is clear you are a good dad. Kudos to you both.
Great video. She did a great job. Congrats to your daughter and to you for being a great dad. She won't forget this day.

Yes she loves hitting the lake with me as much as she can. Thanks for the video feedback as well. I’m going to start making more fishing videos with the kids as much as I can. So much fun to look back on and laugh. Glad everyone enjoyed it
